<p>Dave&rsquo;s back from South by Southwest in Austin and so he shares his thoughts about this year&rsquo;s conference versus previous years. He&rsquo;s also got a new iPad 3 that he and John will talk about, but that still leaves time to share some tips and answer a few of the questions that you and your fellow listeners have sent in. All this and more in today&rsquo;s episode of Mac Geek Gab. Download for free today!</p>
